Troy HACK, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Brett EDWARDS, Edwards Automotive, Defendants-Appellants. No. 18-0795 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed January 9, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Brett Edwards appeals the district court's denial of his challenge to the validity of an out-of-state judgment. REVERSED AND REMANDED.

REVERSED. REMANDED.
